      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a great car for me. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for its next adventure! Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s super comfortable for those daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. If you're looking for something dependable and clean without that 'brand new' price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and tell you more!",
