    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring maximum traction through the corners. The chassis maintains its legendary composure thanks to a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson strut front end. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the platform. While it shows honest wear consistent with its age, the engine pulls strongly across the entire powerband with no hesitation in the variable valve timing. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car for the discerning enthusiast.",
