    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained example of automotive craftsmanship that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin appointed with high-quality leather that shows only light softening on the driver's bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready; it has followed a rigorous service schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of all-season tires installed just last month. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision, providing a confident and quiet ride. This is an ideal choice for a buyer who appreciates a vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for many more miles of reliable service.",
      "price": 34800.0,
